    Tapestry

    Tapestry is an open protocol designed to unify social graph data across various platforms, including Solana, Farcaster, Lens, and ActivityPub. It enables developers to integrate social features into their applications through straightforward APIs, fostering a more open and user-sovereign internet.

It enables developers to integrate social features into their applications through straightforward APIs, fostering a more open and user-sovereign internet.
